videos.description: James Harden says that Austin Rivers "better be alright" after his late injury, talks about how the Rockets won it in OT and provides an update on his eye.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Interview (Harden says his job is to ‘close the game’) 2019/5/4 ESHEET

videos.headline: Harden says his job is to 'close the game'

videos.description: Rockets coach Mike D'Antoni says that when he has James Harden on the floor there's no need to call a timeout and talks about his Game 3 performance.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Presser (D’Antoni says Harden takes ‘a lot of pressure off’) 2019/5/4

videos.headline: D'Antoni says Harden takes 'a lot of pressure off'

videos.description: Kevin Durant struggled to come up with an answer for why his 3-point shot is going down, but he finally credits holding his follow through.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Presser (Durant: I’m holding my follow through on the 3) 2019/05/04

videos.headline: Durant: I'm holding my follow through on the 3

videos.description: Stephen A. Smith credits the Rockets for stepping up, but finds fault in Steph Curry and Klay Thompson for going away from Kevin Durant late.

videos.description: James Harden jokes that his eyes are attracting "a lot of girls" while Chris Paul tells him he looks "crazy."
